{"id":498898,"date":[{"year":1969,"month":10,"day":17}],"page":"4","source":"本报","region":"","masthead":"","special_issue":"","column":"穷棒子精神万岁——记上海绒毯三厂勤俭办厂的动人事迹","genre":"","count":"166","ytitle":"","mtitle":"每一个铜板都要节约","ftitle":"","authors":[],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入6号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1969\\10\\69ah040301.JPG\">"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgsm>革新——自己搞，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"材料——自己找；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"打地脚的“三合土”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"利用业余时间挑。</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入6号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1969\\10\\69ah040302.JPG\">"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgsm>梭子追着机声飞，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红心伴着机声唱；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“下脚棉”织成“争气毯”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"穷棒子精神大发扬!</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入6号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1969\\10\\69ah040303.JPG\">"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgsm>“节约”记心头，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"寸纱拾在手，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"根根接起来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为祖国织锦绣。</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入6号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1969\\10\\69ah040304.JPG\">"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgsm>造厂房——要钢材，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"几十里路忙运输。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"干群高唱节约歌，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"步步走着勤俭路。</FONT>"}]}